      "id": "PopularPost111012",
      "post_content": "This is an interesting wizard. In a deck without black, he is almost strictly worse than a [Merfolk Looter](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Merfolk Looter), since he costs 1 more, and since you have to discard before you see what you're drawing.\n  \n   \nIf you're using the second ability, though, he's helping you dig pretty quickly for a 3-mana creature, and he doesn't look quite as bad.\n  \n   \nNaturally, as a flavour geek, the card appeals to me. This is one of the first cards I saw that explicitly encouraged playing two colours together, and his powers become more impressive if he dabbles in \"the black arts\". I have to give him a thumbs up, even though these days he looks very outclassed. ",
      "posted_by": "Leshrac_Nightwalker",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost111012\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">This is an interesting wizard.  In a deck without black, he is almost strictly worse than a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Merfolk Looter\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Merfolk Looter\">Merfolk Looter</a>, since he costs 1 more, and since you have to discard before you see what you're drawing.  \r<br/> <br/>If you're using the second ability, though, he's helping you dig pretty quickly for a 3-mana creature, and he doesn't look quite as bad.  \r<br/> <br/>Naturally, as a flavour geek, the card appeals to me.  This is one of the first cards I saw that explicitly encouraged playing two colours together, and his powers become more impressive if he dabbles in \"the black arts\".  I have to give him a thumbs up, even though these days he looks very outclassed.  </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '111012'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy2435\">Leshrac_Nightwalker</span>\r\n                                (10/19/2010 1:03:58 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                          